The paper is about transfer learning in reinforcement learning, which is a topic that falls under the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), robotics (cs.RO), systems and control (cs.SY), and computational linguistics (cs.CL). However, since the paper focuses on the development of a novel approach to transfer learning using a self-attentive architecture, it is most likely to be categorized under cs.LG (Machine Learning).
